🐍 Snake Fruits Game
A simple 2D Snake Game built using Python and Pygame, where the snake eats fruits to grow while avoiding collisions.

📌 Game Features
✅ Randomly spawning fruits for the snake to eat
✅ Increasing difficulty as the snake grows
✅ Game Over when the snake collides with itself or the wall
✅ Smooth movement and fun gameplay

🎮 How to Play
1️⃣ Use Arrow Keys (⬆️⬇️⬅️➡️) to move the snake.
2️⃣ Eat the fruits to grow and increase your score.
3️⃣ Avoid hitting the walls or yourself.
4️⃣ The game ends when the snake collides with itself or the boundary.

🛠️ Technologies Used
Python 🐍
Pygame 🎮
